          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-a2373e2bfd5cfcd8",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "st $200 across your CIBC eAdvantage Savings Accounts with the same accountholders to earn Smart Interest on balances up to $200,000.\nExample:\u00a0Sarah deposited $250 in her account and made a CIBC ATM withdrawal of $50 within the same month.\u00a0Sarah was charged a $5 transaction fee for the withdrawal. Her\u00a0account balance at the end of the month was $195. Sarah's monthly balance growth is $200, as the $5 transaction fee is not counted when determining her\u00a0balance growth. Sarah will earn Smart Interest on her account balance this month.\nWe'll deposit Smart Interest into\u00a0your CIBC eAdvantage Savings Account between the first 5 to 7 business days of the following month. This transaction will appear as \u201cSmart Interest\u201d on your\u00a0statement.\nIf\u00a0you have multiple accounts with the same accountholders, you will need to save $200 or more a month across all of your accounts to qualify for Smart Interest.",
